Package library

Describes library objects of a printed circuit board such as padstacks and component packages.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardLibrary
    Describes a board library of packages and padstacks.
    LogicalPart
    Contains contain information for gate swap and pin swap for a single component.
    LogicalPart.PartPin  
    LogicalParts
    The logical parts contain information for gate swap and pin swap.
    Package
    Component package templates describing the padstacks and relative locations of the packege pins, and optional other stuff like an outline package keepouts.

    Package.Pin
    Describes a pin padstack of a package.
    Packages
    Describes a library of component packages.
    Padstack
    Describes padstack masks for pins or vias located at the origin.
    Padstacks
    Describes a library of padstacks for pins or vias.
